longBusinessSummary: China Rongzhong Financial Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial leasing services in the People's Republic of China. The company focuses on financing the needs of SMEs in Hubei province. It provides financial leasing services in the categories of sales and leaseback, and direct financial leasing. The company also offers valued added services, such as due diligence, credit investigation, and debt collection services in Hong Kong, China, and Singapore. It primarily serves laser processing, plastics, industrial processing, textile and garments, hotel and leisure, and other industries. China Rongzhong Financial Holdings Company Limited was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Hongkong, Hongkong.
